<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_468_r3l1">Der Stat cʒu Eger </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_468_r3l2"><expan>Lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> freund / vns iſt fürkumen vvie Jr heıncʒen Reitenbach vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_468_r3l3">Nẏckel langen vnd ettlich <expan>ande<ex>r</ex></expan> gefangen habt die beẏ der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_468_r3l5">ſchäden geweſen ſind vnd Jn das Jr <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> daʒ Jr 
<del rend="strikethrough"> darcʒu </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_468_r3l4">durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vvılle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_468_r3l6"><expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> halten vvollet an </del> in venknüſʒ halten vnd verſuchen laſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_468_r3l7">vvöllet / So vvöllen die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_468_r1l1">dıe das antrifft </ab><ab facs="#facs_468_r1l2">mit <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> / </ab></add> nach Jn <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> als recht iſt / vnd vvas </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_468_line_1576407632159_1923">auch 
<del rend="strikethrough">der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> vaſ diſer <expan>gegenw<ex>er</ex>tig</expan></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_468_r3l8">
<del rend="strikethrough">fricʒ lochner </del> heincʒ <expan>huber</expan> </ab></add>
<add><ab facs="#facs_468_r1l3">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>gena<ex>n</ex>t</expan> N </del></ab></add> vveiſer dicʒ <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan> von der <expan>ſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_468_r3l11">ſache vvegen cʒu diſem mal an ew vverbe / des gelaubt Jm das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_468" id="233v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der stat czu Eger </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> freund, uns ist fürkumen, wie ir Heinczen
                        Reitenbach und Nyckel Langen und ettlich <expan>ande<ex>r</ex></expan>
                        gefangen habt, die bey der <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> schäden gewesen
                        sind und in das ir <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus,</ex></expan> daz ir
                            <add>durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan></add>
<expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> in venknüsz halten und versuchen lassen
                        wöllet, so wöllen die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n,</expan>
<add>die das antrifft, mit <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan></add> nach in
                            <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan>, als recht ist, und was auch <add>Heincz
                                <expan>Huber,</expan></add> weiser dicz
                            <expan>br<ex>iefs,</ex></expan> von der <expan>selb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        sache wegen czu disem mal an ew werbe, des gelaubt im. Das
                                <expan>wolle<ex>n.</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
